import openpyxl 

def read_from_spreadsheet(file_name):  
    # Load the workbook  
    wb = openpyxl.load_workbook(filename= file_name) 
    
    # Select the active sheet (Sheet1 by default)  
    ws = wb.active 

    # Read the data in a list of lists
    data_list = []
    for row in range(ws.max_row): 
        data_list.append(ws[str(row+2)]).tolist()
    
    return data_list
